        </h2></legend>
        <div class="row"><div class="column hcwi"><div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
  <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="Thu, 08 Aug 2024 02:15:40 +0000">
  <meta itemprop="dateModified" content="Thu, 08 Aug 2024 02:15:40 +0000">
  <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person">
    <meta itemprop="name" content="Lauren Irwin, KTLA 5">
  </span>
  <div class="card-content">
    <div class="image" role="presentation">
      <img src="/static9/us/2024/08/08/family-of-man-who-died-in-titan-sub-implosion-sues-oceangate-for-50-million.webp" alt="Family of man who died in Titan sub implosion sues OceanGate for $50 million"
           itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
           referrerpolicy="no-referrer" >
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Family of man who died in Titan sub implosion sues OceanGate for $50 million</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      The lawsuit was filed in King County, Washington, against the underwater exploration company that intended to bring five people to the wreck site of the Titanic at the bottom of the ocean in June 2023.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/us/2024/08/08/family-of-man-who-died-in-titan-sub-implosion-sues-oceangate-for-50-million/"  >(Lauren Irwin, KTLA 5)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div><div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
  <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="Wed, 07 Aug 2024 19:57:24 +0000">
  <meta itemprop="dateModified" content="Wed, 07 Aug 2024 19:57:24 +0000">
  <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person">
    <meta itemprop="name" content="The Associated Press, ABC 4">
  </span>
  <div class="card-content">
    <div class="image" role="presentation">
      <img src="/static9/us/2024/08/07/family-explorer-died-titan-sub-implosion-wrongful-death-lawsuit.webp" alt="Family of explorer who died in the Titan sub implosion seeks over $50M in wrongful death lawsuit"
           itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
           referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Family of explorer who died in the Titan sub implosion seeks over $50M in wrongful death lawsuit</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      Known as “Mr. Titanic,” Nargeolet had visited the Titanic site many times before and was regarded as one of the world’s most knowledgeable people about the famous wreck.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/us/2024/08/07/family-explorer-died-titan-sub-implosion-wrongful-death-lawsuit/"  >(The Associated Press, ABC 4)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div><div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
  <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="Thu, 08 Aug 2024 04:41:56 +0000">
  <meta itemprop="dateModified" content="Thu, 08 Aug 2024 04:41:56 +0000">
  <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person">
    <meta itemprop="name" content="YURAS KARMANAU, Associated Press, PHL 17">
  </span>
  <div class="card-content">
    <div class="image" role="presentation">
      <img src="/static9/us/2024/08/08/relatives-of-belarus-political-prisoners-complain-that-east-west-swap-didnt-free-their-loved-ones.webp" alt="Relatives of Belarus' political prisoners complain that East-West swap didn't free their loved ones"
           itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
           referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Relatives of Belarus' political prisoners complain that East-West swap didn't free their loved ones</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      TALLINN, Estonia (AP) — A wave of disappointment swept over opposition activists in Belarus last week as the biggest East-West prisoner swap since the Cold War unfolded and they learned it included none of the hundreds of political detainees who've been locked up for years by its authoritarian leade
      <a itemprop="url" href="/us/2024/08/08/relatives-of-belarus-political-prisoners-complain-that-east-west-swap-didnt-free-their-loved-ones/"  >(YURAS KARMANAU, Associated Press, PHL 17)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div></div><div class="column vcwi"><div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
  <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="Thu, 08 Aug 2024 04:23:31 +0000">
  <meta itemprop="dateModified" content="Thu, 08 Aug 2024 04:23:31 +0000">
  <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person">
    <meta itemprop="name" content="DARLENE SUPERVILLE, JOEY CAPPELLETTI and MEG KINNARD, Associated Press, KLAS, CBS News">
  </span>
  <div class="card-content">
    <div class="image" role="presentation">
      <img src="/static9/us/2024/08/08/harris-pick-of-walz-amps-up-excitement-in-midwestern-states-where-democrats-look-to-heal-divisions.webp" alt="Harris and Walz say they're 'joyful warriors,' narrowly avoid confrontation with Vance on tarmac"
           itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
           referrerpolicy="no-referrer" >
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Harris and Walz say they're 'joyful warriors,' narrowly avoid confrontation with Vance on tarmac</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      ROMULUS, Mich. (AP) — Vice President Kamala Harris declared herself and her new running mate, Minnesota Gov. Tim Walz, “joyful warriors" against Donald Trump on Wednesday as they spent their first full day campaigning together across the Midwest.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/us/2024/08/08/harris-pick-of-walz-amps-up-excitement-in-midwestern-states-where-democrats-look-to-heal-divisions/"  >(DARLENE SUPERVILLE, JOEY CAPPELLETTI and MEG KINNARD, Associated Press, KLAS, CBS News)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div></div><div class="column text"><div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
  <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="Wed, 07 Aug 2024 23:51:44 +0000">
  <meta itemprop="dateModified" content="Wed, 07 Aug 2024 23:51:44 +0000">
  <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person">
    <meta itemprop="name" content="The Associated Press, KGET 17, NBC">
  </span>
  <div class="card-content">
    <div class="image" role="presentation">
      <img src="/static9/us/2024/08/07/the-latest-tropical-storm-debby-hovers-off-the-coast-of-the-carolinas.webp" alt="The Latest: Tropical Storm Debby lingering over Georgia and the Carolinas"
           itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
           referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">The Latest: Tropical Storm Debby lingering over Georgia and the Carolinas</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      Tropical Storm Debby was lingering over coastal Georgia and the Carolinas on Wednesday, still dumping torrential rain in places before moving north. The system has already stirred up tornadoes and submerged streets in waist-high floodwaters.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/us/2024/08/07/the-latest-tropical-storm-debby-hovers-off-the-coast-of-the-carolinas/"  >(The Associated Press, KGET 17, NBC)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div><div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
  <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="Thu, 08 Aug 2024 04:39:31 +0000">
  <meta itemprop="dateModified" content="Thu, 08 Aug 2024 04:39:31 +0000">
  <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person">
    <meta itemprop="name" content="Lauren Irwin, ABC 4">
  </span>
  <div class="card-content">
    <div class="image" role="presentation">
      <img src="/static9/us/2024/08/08/nearly-1-million-in-harris-walz-camo-hats-sold-since-tuesday-launch.webp" alt="Nearly $1 million in Harris-Walz camo hats sold since Tuesday launch"
           itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
           referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Nearly $1 million in Harris-Walz camo hats sold since Tuesday launch</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      The campaign said it had originally printed 3,000 hats and it sold out in less than 30 minutes. The hat sold for $40 and was American and union made.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/us/2024/08/08/nearly-1-million-in-harris-walz-camo-hats-sold-since-tuesday-launch/"  >(Lauren Irwin, ABC 4)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div><div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
  <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="Thu, 08 Aug 2024 04:45:59 +0000">
  <meta itemprop="dateModified" content="Thu, 08 Aug 2024 04:45:59 +0000">
  <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person">
    <meta itemprop="name" content="Liz Jassin, NewsNation">
  </span>
  <div class="card-content">
    <div class="image" role="presentation">
      <img src="/static9/us/2024/08/08/taylor-swift-concert-threat-proves-were-not-safe-ex-fbi-agent.webp" alt="Taylor Swift concert threat proves 'we're not safe': Ex-FBI agent"
           itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
           referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Taylor Swift concert threat proves 'we're not safe': Ex-FBI agent</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      Retired FBI Special Agent Rob D'Amico warns that the Taylor Swift concert threat "brings into reality that we're not safe.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/us/2024/08/08/taylor-swift-concert-threat-proves-were-not-safe-ex-fbi-agent/"  >(Liz Jassin, NewsNation)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div></div></div></fieldset><fieldset><legend><h2>
