           itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
           referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Romania appeals controversial Olympic gymnastics score that resulted in historic podium</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      The Romanian Olympic and Sports Committee announced on Wednesday that it will be appealing a controversial score in the women&apos;s gymnastics floor final.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/sports/2024/08/07/romania-appeals-controversial-olympic-gymnastics-score-resulted-historic-podium/"  >(Fox News)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
