           itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
           referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">USA Men's volleyball to play for bronze after Poland defeat</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      The veteran U.S. squad will play for bronze against the loser of the late match Wednesday between Italy and France, while Poland plays for the title Saturday against the winner.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/sports/2024/08/07/usa-mens-volleyball-to-play-for-bronze-after-poland-defeat/"  >(The Associated Press, KGET 17, NBC)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
