      <img src="/static9/sports/2024/08/07/the-land-of-usain-bolt-is-racking-up-medals-in-field-events-including-olympic-discus-gold.webp" alt="The land of Usain Bolt is racking up medals in field events, including Olympic discus gold"
           itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
           referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">The land of Usain Bolt is racking up medals in field events, including Olympic discus gold</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      SAINT-DENIS, France (AP) — Don't look now, but Jamaica, that Caribbean island known for producing elite sprinters such as Usain Bolt and Shelly-Ann Fraser-Pryce, is now a field-event power.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/sports/2024/08/07/the-land-of-usain-bolt-is-racking-up-medals-in-field-events-including-olympic-discus-gold/"  >(PAT GRAHAM, Associated Press, KGET 17, NBC)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div></div><div class="column text"><div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
  <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="Wed, 07 Aug 2024 23:54:01 +0000">
  <meta itemprop="dateModified" content="Wed, 07 Aug 2024 23:54:01 +0000">
  <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person">
