      <img src="/static9/sports/2024/08/07/texas-southern-focuses-on-football-iq-in-fall-camp.webp" alt="Texas Southern focuses on football IQ in fall camp"
           itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
           referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Texas Southern focuses on football IQ in fall camp</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      The Texas Southern Tigers are looking to Cris Dishman to pull the program out of a malaise that’s stretched back a decade. Dishman took over for Clarence McKinney, who had a 12-35 record with the Tigers. One focus Dishman is working on early in camp is to raise they team’s football IQ.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/sports/2024/08/07/texas-southern-focuses-on-football-iq-in-fall-camp/"  >(Ari Alexander, KPRC 2)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
