  <meta itemprop="dateModified" content="Thu, 08 Aug 2024 05:10:13 +0000">
  <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person">
    <meta itemprop="name" content="Beth Harris, Associated Press, Local 4">
  </span>
  <div class="card-content">
    <div class="image" role="presentation">
      <img src="/static9/sports/2024/08/08/kyle-schwarber-hits-3-homers-drives-in-7-runs-as-phillies-rally-past-dodgers-9-4.webp" alt="Kyle Schwarber hits 3 homers, drives in 7 runs as Phillies rally past Dodgers, 9-4"
           itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
           referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Kyle Schwarber hits 3 homers, drives in 7 runs as Phillies rally past Dodgers, 9-4</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      Kyle Schwarber hit three homers and drove in seven runs, helping the Philadelphia Phillies rally to beat the Los Angeles Dodgers 9-4 on Wednesday night.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/sports/2024/08/08/kyle-schwarber-hits-3-homers-drives-in-7-runs-as-phillies-rally-past-dodgers-9-4/"  >(Beth Harris, Associated Press, Local 4)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
