           itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
           referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Hinsdale Little League advances to Little League World Series</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      HINSDALE, Ill. — The Village of Hinsdale’s Little League team punched their ticket to the Little League World Series Wednesday, and a team watch party was organized in the western suburbs for family and friends to support them as they played against Jasper, Indiana.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/sports/2024/08/07/hinsdale-little-league-team-one-win-away-from-little-league-world-series/"  >(Christine Flores, WGN 9)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
