           itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
           referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Judge blocks City Council lawsuit seeking to expand rental assistance: What to know</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      NEW YORK (PIX11) – A judge struck down a City Council-backed lawsuit attempting to force Mayor Eric Adams to expand a housing voucher program known as CityFHEPS. CityFHEPS helps people find and keep housing and is administered by the Department of Social Services.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/politics/2024/08/02/judge-blocks-city-council-lawsuit-seeking-to-expand-rental-assistance-what-to-know/"  >(Erin Pflaumer, PIX 11)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
