           itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
           referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Johnson calls on Biden to release weapons to Israel following rocket attack on US base</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      Speaker Mike Johnson (R-La.) called on President Biden to release weapons to Israel after a suspected rocket attack injured several U.S. service members on the Al-Asad Airbase in Iraq.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/politics/2024/08/06/johnson-calls-on-biden-to-release-weapons-to-israel-following-rocket-attack-on-us-base/"  >(Emily Brooks, NewsNation)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div></div><div class="column hcwi"><div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
