      <img src="/static9/politics/2024/08/07/walz-doesnt-own-any-stocks-or-real-estate-disclosures-reveal.webp" alt="Walz doesn't own any stocks or real estate, disclosures reveal"
           itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
           referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Walz doesn't own any stocks or real estate, disclosures reveal</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      Minnesota Gov. Tim Walz does not own any stocks, securities or real estate, per the newly minted Democratic vice presidential candidate's most recent financial disclosures.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/politics/2024/08/07/walz-doesnt-own-any-stocks-or-real-estate-disclosures-reveal/"  >(Jared Gans, KGET 17, NBC)</a>
